Good Hair

At the end of the day, however, Burgum has the central casting look. =E2=80=
=9CHe=E2=80=99s very seriously looking at each candidate=E2=80=99s hair,=E2=
=80=9D said a source with knowledge of Trump=E2=80=99s thinking. =E2=80=9CD=
oug=E2=80=99s got great hair; that=E2=80=99s what he demands in his V.P.=E2=
=80=9D Vance=E2=80=99s beard may also be an issue, even though Trump told F=
ox News, =E2=80=9CIt looks good. It looks like a young Abraham Lincoln.=E2=
=80=9D But another source close to Trump told me, =E2=80=9CTrump hates faci=
al hair; he fucking hates it. He likes the all-American look.=E2=80=9D

For those who know Trump well, they believe he=E2=80=99ll go with Burgum fo=
r his Pence-ian fealty and his lack of ambition. =E2=80=9CYou=E2=80=99re ha=
nding over this entire MAGA universe that Trump built to someone who was no=
t on board,=E2=80=9D said one Trump consultant, pointing to the time Vance =
called Trump =E2=80=9CAmerica=E2=80=99s Hitler.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CJ.D. is
going to be running for office on day one. Burgum has no consultants around=
 him; he=E2=80=99s not a threat.=E2=80=9D Another source explained it more =
simply: =E2=80=9CThe Burgums just look the part.=E2=80=9D

Whomever Trump chooses, the G.O.P. ticket will be on the stage in seven day=
s at Fiserv Forum, home of the Milkwaukee Bucks. All of the Trump children =
have been invited to speak. Ivanka, who recently broke her silence about he=
r father on the friendly shores of Lex Fridman=E2=80=99s podcast, has decli=
ned, I=E2=80=99m told. She=E2=80=99ll be there for Trump=E2=80=99s acceptan=
ce speech on Thursday, but not in an official capacity like Tiffany, Barron=
, and Don Jr., who are acting as delegates.

As for Ron DeSantis, who agreed to bury the hatchet with Trump and fundrais=
e in exchange for a speaking slot at the convention=E2=80=94he only landed =
a spot after a =E2=80=9Cchange in schedule,=E2=80=9D certainly meant to emb=
arrass him. =E2=80=9CRon DeSantis needs to be relevant. He needs to
rehabilitate himself with MAGA, so he needs a spot at the convention,=E2=80=
=9D said a source who was involved in the reunion. Nikki Haley, who recentl=
y released her delegates, is not attending the R.N.C., I=E2=80=99m told. =
=E2=80=9CShe=E2=80=99s been waiting to be asked to speak at the convention=
=E2=80=94she won=E2=80=99t ask,=E2=80=9D said a source. =E2=80=9CIf she doe=
sn=E2=80=99t get a speaking role at the convention, that=E2=80=99s it for h=
er.=E2=80=9D But that might be safer than being booed.

