ing themselves on fire.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/>Trump may also be distracted by =
a hard choice of his own: whom to pick as his vice president. With just day=
s remaining until the Republican National Convention begins on Monday, Trum=
p is leveraging the suspense for attention and driving advisors =E2=80=9Cnu=
