 should wait as long as possible, to confirm who he is running against. =E2=
=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s like trying to read smoke signals; he=E2=80=99s very mer=
curial. He changed his mind three times in 2016 before settling on <b>Pence=
</b>,=E2=80=9D said a longtime advisor. =E2=80=9CHe=E2=80=99s going to do i=
t at the convention as late as possible.
He=E2=80=99s the master of the tease. He=E2=80=99s going to milk it.=E2=80=
=9D<br/><br/>Trump was expected to announce his running mate sometime befor=
