aturday in Western Pennsylvania. But the R.N.C. just changed a rule that wi=
ll now allow him to wait until the last minute on Thursday, just before he =
accepts the nomination. <br/><br/>The truth, I=E2=80=99m told by multiple s=
ources, is that Trump doesn=E2=80=99t really care for Burgam <i>or</i> Vanc=
e, and he doesn=E2=80=99t see a running mate as a net benefit to his campai=
gn. The idea of a vice presidential candidate receiving even <i>a drop</i> =
of credit for a Trump win in November irks him. =E2=80=9CHe doesn=E2=80=99t=
 give much of a fuck about it. He doesn=E2=80=99t love any of these people;=
 he doesn=E2=80=99t know these people,=E2=80=9D said the same gloating Mar-=
a-Lago denizen. =E2=80=9CWith Burgum, he likes his look, but they haven=E2=
=80=99t actually spent a
