=80=99t spend time with J.D. He didn=E2=80=99t give a fuck about <b>Mike Pe=
nce</b>.=E2=80=9D Trump does have a strong relationship with<b> Marco Rubio=
</b>, who=E2=80=99s kept himself in the running thanks to the advocacy of <=
b>Kellyanne Conway</b> and <b>Susie Wiles</b>. If not veep, I=E2=80=99m hea=
ring he could be on the shortlist for secretary of state.<br/><br/>Another =
source with knowledge of Trump=E2=80=99s veep deliberations said it=E2=80=
=99s come down to a battle between <b>Melania</b>, who prefers Burgum becau=
se she <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1=
lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRcEoxOXgzeDRDd2pmbnhmb3didz0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrL=
m5ld3Mvd2lsbC1kb3VnLWJ1cmd1bS1iZS10cnVtcHMtdmljZS1wcmVzaWRlbnQvP3V0bV9jYW1w=
